---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section s3-iv-types">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="s3-iv-types__heading">Find Your Specialized IV Therapy</h2>

    <div class="s3-iv-types__grid">

      <div class="s3-iv-types__card">
        <div class="s3-iv-types__card-body">
          <h3 class="s3-iv-types__card-title">Pain Management &amp; Autoimmune Disease Drip</h3>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-tagline">For Support With: Chronic Pain, Autoimmune Flare-Ups, Systemic Inflammation.</p>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-desc">This powerful drip is designed for those dealing with chronic pain, autoimmune diseases, and systemic inflammation. Packed with antioxidants and anti-inflammatory agents, it aims to support your body's response to these challenging conditions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-iv-types__card">
        <div class="s3-iv-types__card-body">
          <h3 class="s3-iv-types__card-title">Heart Health &amp; Diabetes Drip</h3>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-tagline">For Support With: Cardiovascular Wellness, Healthy Circulation, Blood Sugar Regulation.</p>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-desc">Formulated to support cardiovascular health and blood sugar regulation. This drip contains a blend of amino acids, antioxidants, and essential nutrients that support healthy circulation and metabolic function.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-iv-types__card">
        <div class="s3-iv-types__card-body">
          <h3 class="s3-iv-types__card-title">Prenatal/Pregnancy/Fertility Drip</h3>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-tagline">For Support With: Fertility Journeys, Prenatal Nutrition, Postpartum Recovery.</p>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-desc">A specially formulated drip for those on a fertility journey or navigating the demands of pregnancy and postpartum recovery. Contains essential folate, vitamins, and minerals to support both mother and baby.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-iv-types__card">
        <div class="s3-iv-types__card-body">
          <h3 class="s3-iv-types__card-title">Gut Health (IBS, UC, Crohn's) Drip</h3>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-tagline">For Support With: Leaky Gut, Malabsorption, Digestive Inflammation (IBS, UC, Crohn's).</p>
          <p class="s3-iv-types__card-desc">Designed to support gut health from the inside out. This drip delivers anti-inflammatory nutrients directly into the bloodstream, bypassing the digestive system to support those with leaky gut, malabsorption issues, and digestive inflammation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-iv-types__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-iv-types__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s3-iv-types__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .s3-iv-types__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .s3-iv-types__card-body {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .s3-iv-types__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-iv-types__card-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .s3-iv-types__card-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-iv-types__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s3-iv-types__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .s3-iv-types__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
